.       estimates use $estimates_dir/va_cfr_all_v1/sum_stats/counts_k12_`sample
> '_g11_`subject'.ster
  6.       eststo g11_`subject'_count
  7.       matrix mat_count_`subject' = e(count)
  8.       estadd matrix mat_stat = mat_count_`subject'
  9. 
.       estimates use $estimates_dir/va_cfr_all_v1/sum_stats/z_score_k12_`sampl
> e'_g11_`subject'.ster
 10.       eststo g11_`subject'_z_score
